pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$primary"
elements:
  # Top nav bar
  - elementId: nav-left
    elementType: text
    bounds: [120, 28, 260, 52]
    content:
      style: "$nav"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Marketing</p>
        <p>Approach</p>

  - elementId: nav-right
    elementType: text
    bounds: [900, 28, 260, 52]
    content:
      style: "$nav"
      align: [right, top]
      text: |
        <p>Bilson's</p>
        <p>Supermarkets</p>

  - elementId: nav-divider
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [120, 88, 1040, 1]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$text"

  # Left: large bold title + body
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 150, 560, 240]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>AN INTRODUCTION</strong></p>
        <p><strong>TO BILSON</strong></p>

  - elementId: left-subtitle
    elementType: text
    bounds: [100, 400, 480, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      align: [left, top]
      text: From farmers' markets to a national chain

  # Arrow
  - elementId: arrow
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [100, 502, 100, 28]
    iconName: "fas:arrow-right"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$text"

  # Right: body text
  - elementId: right-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 280, 460, 220]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      lineHeight: 1.65
      text: |
        <p>Presentations are communication tools that can be used</p>
        <p>as demonstrations, lectures, speeches, reports, and more.</p>
        <p>It is mostly presented before an audience.</p>

  - elementId: right-body-2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 520, 460, 140]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      lineHeight: 1.65
      text: |
        <p>It serves a variety of purposes, making presentations</p>
        <p>powerful tools for convincing and teaching.</p>
